pre_self_pos_issue_10	6	Maintaining the current mix of sustainable and fossil energy
pre_self_pos_issue_11	Variable Label	ISSUE 11: SURVEILLANCE MEASURES: SELF-POSITION
pre_self_pos_issue_11	1	Surveillance measures should be extended
pre_self_pos_issue_11	6	Surveillance measures should not be extended
