pre_self_pos_issue_12	1	Austria should have a property tax on inheritance
pre_self_pos_issue_12	6	Austria should not have a property tax on inheritance
pre_self_pos_issue_13	Variable Label	ISSUE 13: WORK REGULATIONS: SELF-POSITION
pre_self_pos_issue_13	1	Deregulate the job market
pre_self_pos_issue_13	6	Keep current regulations in the job market
pre_self_pos_issue_14	Variable Label	ISSUE 14: DIRECT DEMOCRACY: SELF-POSITION
pre_self_pos_issue_14	1	Introduce stronger direct democracy measures
pre_self_pos_issue_14	6	Keep current level of direct democracy measures
pre_self_pos_issue_15	Variable Label	ISSUE 15: DIESEL: SELF-POSITION
pre_self_pos_issue_15	1	Diesel cars should be banned
pre_self_pos_issue_15	6	No cars should be banned
pre_self_pos_issue_16	Variable Label	ISSUE 16: EU REFUGEE QUOTAS: SELF-POSITION
pre_self_pos_issue_16	1	The EU has to enforce refugee quotas in all member states
pre_self_pos_issue_16	6	Each member state of the EU should decide by its own on refugee quotas
pre_self_pos_issue_17	Variable Label	ISSUE 17: EU FREEDOM OF MOVEMENT: SELF-POSITION
pre_self_pos_issue_17	1	End freedom of movement of people from the EU into Austria
pre_self_pos_issue_17	6	Allow freedom of movement of people from the EU into Austria
pre_self_pos_issue_18	Variable Label	ISSUE 18: EU MEMBERSHIP: SELF-POSITION
pre_self_pos_issue_18	1	Stay in the EU
pre_self_pos_issue_18	6	Leave the EU
