pre_self_pos_issue_2	1	Keep current pension age
pre_self_pos_issue_2	6	Increase pension age
pre_self_pos_issue_20	Variable Label	ISSUE 20: SOCIAL PARTNERS: SELF-POSITION
pre_self_pos_issue_20	1	Austria should abolish the obligatory membership in trade associations (social partners)
pre_self_pos_issue_20	6	Austria should not abolish the obligatory membership in trade associations (social partners)
pre_self_pos_issue_21	Variable Label	ISSUE 21: UNEMPLOYMENT VS. NATIONAL DEBT: SELF-POSITION
pre_self_pos_issue_21	1	Decrease unemployment needs at the expense of high national debt
pre_self_pos_issue_21	6	Do not decrease unemployment at the expense of high national debt
pre_self_pos_issue_3	Variable Label	ISSUE 3: INCOME DIFFERENCES: SELF-POSITION
pre_self_pos_issue_3	1	Reduce income differences
pre_self_pos_issue_3	6	Don't reduce income differences
