pre_self_pos_issue_4	1	Raise taxes and spend more on health and social services
pre_self_pos_issue_4	6	Cut taxes and spend less on health and social services
pre_self_pos_issue_5	Variable Label	ISSUE 5: GENDER QUOTAS: SELF-POSITION
pre_self_pos_issue_5	1	Politics should implement gender quota in order guarantee that all important jobs are equally given to women and men
pre_self_pos_issue_5	6	Politics should not enforce gender quotas
